# Output directory for the screenshot pipeline.
# Actual PNGs (raw/ and <locale>/<device>/*.png) are .gitignored at the repo root.
# This placeholder keeps the directory in git so the capture scripts can write
# here without first calling `mkdir -p` on a path users may not expect to exist.
#
# Pipeline:
#   tools/ci/scripts/capture-screenshots.sh
#     → marketing/screenshots/raw/<device>/<NN>.png           (uncommitted)
#     → marketing/screenshots/<locale>/<device>/<NN>-<slug>.png (uncommitted)
